modName: Legend of the Frost tavern music
summary: A simple mod to make Miracle of Sound\'s song \"Legends of the Frost\" play in taverns.
descriptionHtml:
A simple mod to make Miracle of Sound\'s song \"Legends of the Frost\" play in taverns. 

Just copy the contents of your \"data\" folder over into your Skyrim\'s data folder.
author: TJ5897
